(registered 2015-09-16, last updated 2015-09-16)

Resource Identifier (RI) Scheme name:
ms-secondary-screen-controller:

Status:
provisional

Scheme syntax:
ms-secondary-screen-controller:

Scheme semantics:
Launches an application meant to control a secondary screen.

Encoding considerations:
Unknown, use with care

Applications/protocols that use this scheme name:
Continuum application in some Windows Phones

Interoperability considerations:
None

Security considerations:
None

